traits.description: Increase final damage by **13%**. When **Pine Comet** is in the off-hand slot, the cooldown for the damage dealt by **sparrowfeather** is decreased to **1** second.

Increase final damage by **18%**. When **Pine Comet** is in the off-hand slot, the cooldown for the damage dealt by **sparrowfeather** is decreased to **1** second. When triggering **sparrowfeather**, aditionally spread **Ion Burn** and **Cross Burn**. While in a party, decrease incoming damage by **5%**. If Fortitude resonance is activated, increase this effect to **8%**.
